window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Magdalena Yoder, chaste and abstemious proprietor of the Pennsylvania Dutch Inn, agrees to let a Hollywood crew film at the inn--for an exorbitant price, of course. </p> <p>But when the assistant director is found pinned to a barn post with a farming tool, dimwitted local police chief Marvin Stoltzfus fingers Magdalena as his prime suspect. </p> <p>Now it's time for Magdalena to use her extraordinary Amish sleuthing skills to reveal the real killer--before another Hollywood hellion goes belly up and turns Magdalena's charming PennDutch Inn into a grisly horror flick! </p>"; 
